H0.text: In tennis, losing two sets 6-0 is known as a double what. Donut

H1.text: In tennis, losing two sets 6-0 is known as a double what. Shutout

H2.text: In tennis, losing two sets 6-0 is known as a double what. Blank

H3.text: In tennis, losing two sets 6-0 is known as a double what. BAGEL

A4.text: For women in Grand Slam tournaments, a double bagel result is possible as the matches are best of three sets.

A5.text: In the Open Era, there has been a women's singles Grand Slam tournament match with a double bagel every year except for in 1968 and 2005.
